#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.70"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.70:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga"
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Catuttharukkhasutta"
msgstr "70. A Tree (4th)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.239"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: kūṭasimbalī → koṭasimbalī (bj, s1-3, km) | kūṭasimbali (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci supaṇṇānaṃ rukkhā, kūṭasimbalī tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, of all the trees belonging to the phoenixes, the red silk-"
"cotton tree is said to be the best."

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāya."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the "
"qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened."

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the qualities that lead to awakening?"

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.4"
msgid ""
"Saddhindriyaṃ, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati … pe …"
" paññindriyaṃ bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom are "
"qualities that lead to awakening, in that they lead to becoming awakened."

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci supaṇṇānaṃ rukkhā, kūṭasimbalī tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr ""
"Of all the trees belonging to the phoenixes, the red silk-cotton tree is "
"said to be the best."

msgctxt "sn48.70:1.6"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the "
"qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.70:1.8"
msgid "Bodhipakkhiyavaggo sattamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.1"
msgid "Saṃyojanā anusayā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.2"
msgid "pariññā āsavakkhayā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.3"
msgid "Dve phalā caturo rukkhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.70:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti."
msgstr ""
